p:::s13:::When Mr. Micawber leaves London to escape his creditors , David decides to search for his father 's sister , Miss Betsey Trotwood -- his only living relative .
p:::s14:::He walks a long distance to Miss Betsey 's home , and she takes him in on the advice of her mentally unstable friend , Mr. Dick .
p:::s15:::Miss Betsey sends David to a school run by a man named Doctor Strong .
p:::s23:::When they return from Yarmouth , Miss Betsey persuades David to pursue a career as a proctor , a kind of lawyer .
p:::s34:::Miss Betsey visits London to inform David that her financial security has been ruined because Mr. Wickfield has joined into a partnership with Uriah Heep .
